此项目，用于制作自定义的python功能，安装包。

1、rknn模型转换、量化项目：
    python安装包制作/onnx_export_rknn

2、创建whl安装包：
    cd python安装包制作/onnx_export_rknn
    python -m build



3、实际模型转换（在toolkit2环境中）

    yolov8_onnx_export：
        yolo_onnx_export \
        -w /home/chenkejing/PycharmProjects/ultralytics/runs/my_carpet_seg_exp/yolov8s_carpet_seg_v1_5/weights/best.pt \
        --input-shape 1 3 640 640 \
        --device cuda:0 \
        --sim

        yolo_onnx_export \
        -w /workspace/data/auto_train_deploy_env/onnx_models/yolov8s_carpet_seg_v1_5/weights/best.pt \
        --input-shape 1 3 640 640 \
        --device cuda:0 \
        --sim

        yolo_onnx_export \
        -w /workspace/data/auto_train_deploy_env/onnx_models/yolov8s_carpet_seg_v1_5/weights/best.pt \
        --input-shape 1 3 640 640 \
        --device cpu \
        --sim





    rknn_export:
        rknn_convert \
        /home/chenkejing/PycharmProjects/ultralytics/runs/my_carpet_seg_exp/yolov8s_carpet_seg_v1_5/weights/best.onnx \
        rk3588 \
        --dataset /home/chenkejing/PycharmProjects/ultralytics/images_mode_test/carpet_real_image/carpet_quant.txt \
        --output model.rknn \
        --quant

    rknn_export:
        rknn_convert \
        /home/chenkejing/PycharmProjects/ultralytics/runs/my_carpet_seg_exp/yolov8s_carpet_seg_v1_5/weights/best.onnx \
        rk3568 \
        --dataset /home/chenkejing/PycharmProjects/ultralytics/images_mode_test/carpet_real_image/carpet_quant.txt \
        --output model_3568.rknn \
        --quant

        rknn_convert \
        /workspace/data/auto_train_deploy_env/onnx_models/yolov8s_carpet_seg_v1_5/weights/best.onnx \
        rk3588 \
        --dataset /workspace/data/auto_train_deploy_env/images_mode_test/carpet_real_image/carpet_quant.txt \
        --output carpet_3588.rknn \
        --quant


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

        docker镜像环境中的指令

        onnx模型转换：
        /opt/venv/bin/yolo_onnx_export \
            -w /workspace/data/auto_train_deploy_env/onnx_models/yolov8s_carpet_seg_v1_5/weights/best.pt \
            --input-shape 1 3 640 640 \
            --device cuda:0 \
            --sim

        rknn模型量化：
            /root/miniconda3/envs/rknn_py38/bin/rknn_convert \
            /workspace/data/auto_train_deploy_env/onnx_models/yolov8s_carpet_seg_v1_5/weights/best.onnx \
            rk3588 \
            --dataset /workspace/data/auto_train_deploy_env/images_mode_test/carpet_real_image/carpet_quant.txt \
            --output carpet_3588.rknn \
            --quant



